'''文森特·林顿'''（{{lang-fr|Vincent Lindon}}，{{bd|1959年|7月15日|catIdx=M}}）是法國男演員、導演、編劇，活躍時間超過30年。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.unifrance.org/directories/person/15691/vincent-lindon|title=Vincent Lindon|publisher=unifrance.org|accessdate=2014-11-07|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322220852/https://en.unifrance.org/directories/person/15691/vincent-lindon|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年，他因演出《衡量一個人》获得[[第68屆坎城影展|第68屆坎城影展]]最佳男演員獎，隔年再獲得[[凱薩獎最佳男主角獎|凱薩獎最佳男主角獎]]、[[盧米埃獎|盧米埃獎]]最佳男演員獎。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/live/2015/may/24/cannes-2015-palme-dor-announcement |title=Cannes 2015: Jacques Audiard's Dheepan wins the Palme d'Or |author=Henry Barnes |date=24 May 2015 |accessdate=24 May 2015 |work=The Guardian |archive-date=2016-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612140348/https://www.theguardian.com/film/live/2015/may/24/cannes-2015-palme-dor-announcement |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-2015-winners-announced-797340 |title=Cannes: 'Dheepan' Wins the Palme d'Or |author=Rebecca Ford |date=24 May 2015 |accessdate=24 May 2015 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612170312/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-2015-winners-announced-797340 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2021年，与[[阿加特·罗素|阿加特·罗素]]主演[[肉体恐怖|肉体恐怖]]剧情《[[钛|钛]]》<ref>{{Cite web |language=en-US |title=‘Titane’ is a Twisted Exploration of Gender, Violence and Metal |url=https://observer.com/2021/09/titane-review-twisted-exploration-of-gender-violence-and-metal/ |website=Observer |date=2021-09-27 |accessdate=2021-10-03 |archive-date=2021-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211014084404/https://observer.com/2021/09/titane-review-twisted-exploration-of-gender-violence-and-metal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

